{"tid":28853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母當我狗呀？","createTime":"2016-12-08T07:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T23:08:44.000Z","uid":17677,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbea5b4d5d7324ca1d8d20ee376a606235f0884","tid":28853,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"咁琴晚我同老婆去食飯(佢唔識煮飯的)<br />\n咁入到餐廳啦 我問佢食乜<br />\n佢玩緊電話唔答我 話是但<br />\n咁我自己幫佢簡埋<br />\n之後野食黎之後同我講其實我想食xxx<br />\n我屌你老母 問你食乜唔撚答 咁我無出聲<br />\n各位巴打可能覺得我唔了解佢 <br />\n雖然我知佢唔鐘意食乜 <br />\n但我唔撚知佢依期想食乜架大佬呀 <br />\n同百佳優惠一撚樣 期期都唔撚同 <br />\n<br />\n咁臨食完個陣叫餐飲<br />\n我問佢飲乜 佢玩緊電話話是但<br />\n我費事又唔岩佢心水 我問多次想飲檸茶？<br />\n佢玩緊電話屌9我叫我咪嘈 收聲 你覺唔覺你好嘈？<br />\n頂你個肺 叫狗呀？<br />\n寫餐飲個阿姐陰陰咀笑<br />\n我之後唔理佢幫佢叫熱檸茶算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩無事平安返家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5449ccfa4489c4378ee0bfe82bad001688db2e","tid":28853,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"好彩今晚我去踢波 唔使同佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都要買野食俾佢先出去"},{"pid":"4e94b0547abcc22d9f9ddf7165a86e76b9032df4","tid":28853,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"比杯水條八婆咪算"},{"pid":"86d2cc13821c874d58f1e22ce22e13a8c6533ca6","tid":28853,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93087fd0b877c6881a7e136f4b7c546f3df63a21","tid":28853,"uid":51034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"死佬 仲唔俾我搵到你上網唱我? 你今晚訓街啦"},{"pid":"63cfdbdda56af2cdae633c07e0f8e5788c258198","tid":28853,"uid":17677,"like":0,"disli